---
title: "Secure Channel: MessageChannel + ECDH P-256 + AES-256-GCM"
---
sequenceDiagram
    Note over D,I: Transport: MessageChannel (point-to-point, not broadcast)<br/>Key Exchange: Ephemeral ECDH P-256 (Web Crypto)<br/>Key Derivation: HKDF-SHA-256, direction-separated keys<br/>Encryption: AES-256-GCM, random 12B IV, UUID as AAD<br/>Replay: UUID deduplication on receiver

    participant D as Dapp SDK
    participant I as Iframe

    D->>I: postMessage({ type: "INIT" }, [port2])
    Note over D,I: MessagePort established — no more broadcast postMessage

    D->>I: { pubKey: appJWK }
    I->>D: { pubKey: iframeJWK }
    Note over D,I: Both sides: ECDH → HKDF → keyA (p2i) + keyB (i2p)

    D->>I: encrypt(keyA, request)
    I->>D: encrypt(keyB, response)
